remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-102">Cuando se habilitan las etiquetas inteligentes, el gráfico cambia de posición que se superponen las etiquetas de puntos de datos, basándose en un conjunto de reglas definidas por el usuario.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-103">Se dibuja líneas de llamada para vincular la etiqueta a su punto de datos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-104">Se pueden controlar los atributos visuales de la línea de llamada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-105">Estos atributos visuales incluyen color, estilo de línea y el ancho de línea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-106">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> y <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> propiedades controlan los adornos, como las puntas de flecha, que aparecen al final de la línea de llamada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-107">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> propiedad puede establecerse en cualquier <xref:System.Drawing.Color> objeto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-108">Si establece el color de la línea de llamada, se establecerá automáticamente el color de la <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> y el adorno definido por el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-109">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> propiedad controla el ancho de píxel de la línea de llamada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-110">Uso de esta propiedad también escalará los adornos de la <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> y <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-111">El movimiento de etiquetas inteligentes puede controlarse mediante el uso de varias propiedades relacionadas con el movimiento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-112">Éstos definen las reglas de movimiento para la dirección, distancia y si el punto de datos etiqueta puede dejar el área de trazado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-113">Las reglas predeterminadas de movimiento normalmente resolverán la mayoría de los problemas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-114">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> define un valor que especifica la distancia máxima, en píxeles, de los datos de punto que se pueden mover en el caso de que se superponen las etiquetas de puntos de datos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-115">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> propiedad define un valor que especifica la distancia mínima en píxeles, de los datos de punto que se moverán las etiquetas de puntos de datos en el caso de que se superponen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-116">Cuando un punto de datos etiqueta debe cambiar de posición, será la etiqueta movido por al menos el número de píxeles especificada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-117">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> propiedad indica si las etiquetas están ocultas cuando los problemas de superposición no se puede resolver.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-118">Si el <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> propiedad es `true`, y el punto de datos no se pueden dibujar dentro del área especificada por <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> y <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> en las direcciones permitidas por <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, no se dibujará la etiqueta del punto de datos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-119">El <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> propiedad define las direcciones en el que se puede mover la etiqueta del punto de datos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-120">Esta propiedad acepta una <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valor o una operación OR bit a bit de varios <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valores.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c939a-121">El valor predeterminado es la operación OR bit a bit de todos los <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valores, para permitir el cambio de posición en todas las posibles direcciones excepto para el centro de datos de punto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c939a-122">No se admiten etiquetas inteligentes para los siguientes tipos de gráfico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c939a-123">Los gráficos de barras: barra y gráficos de barras 100% apiladas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c939a-124">Gráficos de formas: gráficos circulares, de anillos, polar y gráficos radiales.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c939a-125">Rangos de intervalos: intervalo, la columna de intervalo y los gráficos de barras de intervalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="c939a-126">Gráficos de áreas apiladas: apilada, área y gráficos de áreas 100% apiladas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c939a-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
